== Outline, Backgrounds ==

Fiscal 2005 started on July 1st.

At the European Patent Office, Microsoft has already overtaken IBM in the number of software patents, but still falls behind some telecom and consumer electronics giants, see
 * http://swpat.ffii.org/patents/stats/
